<div class="patternContent"><div class="patternTopic"> <h1><a name="For_Documentation_Owners"></a>  <strong>For Documentation Owners</strong> </h1>
<p />
<div class="twikiToc"> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#About_This_Document"> About This Document</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Document_Owner_Responsibilities"> Document Owner Responsibilities</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Useful_Writer_Advice_and_Documen"> Useful Writer Advice and Document Standards</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Tracking_Documents_that_You_Own"> Tracking Documents that You Own</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Additional_Information"> Additional Information</a>
